project: Press A and D to move left and right, Space bar to jump
Make contact with the hexagon to swap into it
Now, press the space bar to switch the direction of gravity, this is the power of the hexagon
All that's left is to complete the level by touching the gold shape!
The rectangle can climb walls by tapping space while next to a wall
The triangle has movement similar to the square but also has a grappling hook
Left click to fire the grapple
